| Action | Message Thread | Audio Thread |
|--------|----------------|--------------|
| Allocate memory | âœ… OK | âŒ Never |
| File I/O | âœ… OK | âŒ Never |
| Lock mutex | âœ… OK | âŒ Never |
| Update UI | âœ… OK | âŒ Never |
